Engine adaptations (not vendored here)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

There is no shootout/vfxforth/ or shootout/swiftforth/ subtree in this
tree. VFXForth / SwiftForth runs adapt the gforth-oriented .fs at runtime
via benchmark/adapt_shootout_for_engine.py (and vfxforth.sh /
swiftforth.sh). That adapter carries no separate copyright/license
block beyond being part of this repository.


